"smart_irrigation" is a project aimed at creating a smart irrigation timer.  The
timer will be programmable through a web interface and will be able to query a
weather API in order to adjust its watering schedule.

########## vc-firm ##########

Contains the firmware for the microcontroller. The microcontroller handles
requests over SPI to open and close valves.

########## yocto ##########

Contains the Yocto Project layer and configuration files.

########## vc-driver ##########

Contains the driver for the microcontroller. The driver handles requests to open
and close valves and forwards them over SPI to the microcontroller.
